BASIC / INFORMASI
---------------------------------------------------
| Fungsi                    | Command             |
| ------------------------- | ------------------- |
| Cek versi Git             | `git --version`     |
| Cek status project        | `git status`        |
| Lihat riwayat commit      | `git log`           |
| Riwayat singkat           | `git log --oneline` |
| Lihat perbedaan perubahan | `git diff`          |
---------------------------------------------------
SETUP AWAL / CONFIG
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Fungsi                | Command                                            |
| --------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Inisialisasi Git      | `git init`                                         |
| Set nama user         | `git config --global user.name "Nama"`             |
| Set email user        | `git config --global user.email "email@gmail.com"` |
| Lihat semua config    | `git config --list`                                |
| Cek credential helper | `git config --global credential.helper`            |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
STAGING & COMMIT
-----------------------------------------------------
| Fungsi                | Command                   |
| --------------------- | ------------------------- |
| Tambah semua file     | `git add .`               |
| Tambah file tertentu  | `git add namafile`        |
| Commit perubahan      | `git commit -m "pesan"`   |
| Batalkan staging file | `git reset namafile`      |
| Undo commit terakhir  | `git reset --soft HEAD~1` |
| Reset total perubahan | `git reset --hard HEAD`   |
-----------------------------------------------------
REMOTE / GITHUB
-------------------------------------------------------
| Fungsi            | Command                         |
| ----------------- | ------------------------------- |
| Cek remote        | `git remote -v`                 |
| Lihat nama remote | `git remote`                    |
| Tambah origin     | `git remote add origin URL`     |
| Ganti origin      | `git remote set-url origin URL` |
| Hapus origin      | `git remote remove origin`      |
| Detail remote     | `git remote show origin`        |
-------------------------------------------------------
PUSH & PULL
-----------------------------------------------------
| Fungsi                | Command                   |
| --------------------- | ------------------------- |
| Push pertama kali     | `git push -u origin main` |
| Push biasa            | `git push`                |
| Paksa push            | `git push --force`        |
| Pull update repo      | `git pull`                |
| Fetch update repo     | `git fetch`               |
| Clone repository      | `git clone URL`           |
| Clone branch tertentu | `git clone -b branch URL` |
-----------------------------------------------------
BRANCH
--------------------------------------------------------
| Fungsi               | Command                       |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Lihat branch         | `git branch`                  |
| Lihat semua branch   | `git branch -a`               |
| Buat branch          | `git branch nama_branch`      |
| Rename branch        | `git branch -m nama_baru`     |
| Rename jadi main     | `git branch -M main`          |
| Hapus branch         | `git branch -d nama_branch`   |
| Paksa hapus branch   | `git branch -D nama_branch`   |
| Pindah branch        | `git checkout nama_branch`    |
| Buat + pindah branch | `git checkout -b nama_branch` |
| Merge branch         | `git merge nama_branch`       |
--------------------------------------------------------
STASH / SIMPAN SEMENTARA
-------------------------------------------------
| Fungsi                     | Command          |
| -------------------------- | ---------------- |
| Simpan perubahan sementara | `git stash`      |
| Kembalikan stash           | `git stash pop`  |
| Lihat daftar stash         | `git stash list` |
-------------------------------------------------
PEMBATALAN / RESTORE
------------------------------------------------------------
| Fungsi                      | Command                    |
| --------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Batalkan perubahan file     | `git checkout -- namafile` |
| Reset file staging          | `git reset namafile`       |
| Undo commit                 | `git reset --soft HEAD~1`  |
| Hapus semua perubahan lokal | `git reset --hard HEAD`    |
------------------------------------------------------------
FILE KHUSUS
---------------------------------------
| Fungsi               | File         |
| -------------------- | ------------ |
| Ignore file/folder   | `.gitignore` |
| Simpan folder kosong | `.gitkeep`   |
